            "id": 5900547,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 宏和(1446)大跌7.11%，報35.95元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>宏和(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1446:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1446\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1446-TW</a>)14日09:01股價下跌2.75元，報35.95元，跌幅7.11%，成交676張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>宏和(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1446:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1446\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1446-TW</a>)所屬產業為紡織纖維，主要業務為紡織。成衣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌12.44%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌3.32%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-245 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-218 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-27 張</li> <li>融資增減：+38 張</li> <li>融券增減：+354 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5900547",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-14 09:01:32",
